import React from "react";
import { Container, Typography, TextField, Button, Grid } from "@mui/material";

const Contact = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
      <Typography variant="h2" align="center" mt={5} mb={3}>
        Contact
      </Typography>

      <Grid container spacing={3}>
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <TextField
            label="Your Name"
            fullWidth
            variant="outlined"
            margin="normal"
          />
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <TextField
            label="Your Email"
            fullWidth
            variant="outlined"
            margin="normal"
          />
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <TextField
            label="Message"
            multiline
            rows={4}
            fullWidth
            variant="outlined"
            margin="normal"
          />
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <Button variant="contained" color="primary">
            Send Message
          </Button>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default Contact;
